OL,6,FA prison worker has been jailed after
OL,7,Fadmitting to having an inappropriate
OL,8,Frelationship with an inmate at a West
OL,9,FCountry prison.
OL,11,FHeidi Bessant, 38, of Wyebank Rise in
OL,12,FChepstow, pleaded guilty to misconduct
OL,13,Fin a public office and was sentenced
OL,14,Fto six months in prison.
OL,16,FShe worked as a Prison Operational
OL,17,FSupport Grade (OSG), supporting the
OL,18,Fwork of the prison officers, based at
OL,19,FHMP Leyhill in South Gloucestershire.
