OL,3,CPrison worker jailed after
OL,4,Cinappropriate relationship with inmate
OL,6,FBetween November 2023 and June 2024,
OL,7,FBessant was in a relationship with a
OL,8,Fman who was serving time at the
OL,9,Fcategory D open prison for conspiracy
OL,10,Fto supply class A drugs and blackmail.
OL,12,FShe exchanged phone calls and text
OL,13,Fmessages with the prisoner using a
OL,14,Fmobile phone he shouldn't have had,
OL,15,Fand would spend time at hotels and
OL,16,Frestaurants when the prisoner was on
OL,17,Fday release.
OL,19,FOn many occasions, Bessant would pick
OL,20,Fup the man from the prison and return
OL,21,Fhim later the same day.
