OL,6,FAdditionally, Bessant facilitated the
OL,7,Fdeposit of money into the inmate's
OL,8,Fprison bank account using his bank
OL,9,Fcard details.
OL,11,FPC Mark Paterson, Corruption
OL,12,FInvestigator at South West Regional
OL,13,FOrganised Crime Unit (SWROCU), said:
OL,14,F"Bessant's role as an OSG meant she
OL,15,Fhad a duty to conduct herself in a
OL,16,Fresponsible, respectable and
OL,17,Ftrustworthy manner. Instead, her
OL,18,Fconduct amounted to a serious breach
OL,19,Fof trust.
